sub_title: Content Creative | Editor bij De Smaak van Italië | University of Applied Sciences, Creative Business
summary:
I enjoy helping brands grow by creating a strong identity and effective presence - online and beyond. Specialised in developing content strategy's, creating innovative content and optimizing the corporate identity to increase conversion and engagement.

I studied Media & Communications in Utrecht and then went to the University of Applied Sciences in Amsterdam. I worked on projects for different brands including Philips, LINDA, Gemeente Amsterdam, Wereldnatuurfonds and more. Giving me a sharp understanding of how to connect with several audiences.

Knowledge how to shape tone of voices and create multi-channel tailored content including social media, print and digital magazines, film and lookbooks. My interest in creativity is accompanied with the thrill of production; I like the creation process and enjoy brainstorming about innovative opportunities.

If you are looking for someone to help hone tone of voice, do a re-styling, devise a strategy for social media optimisation or to crystalise brand identity; get in touch.
